0</Width><Height>240</Height><Bytes>0</Bytes><Caption /><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/7/IST-LARhotel_Other_2_thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>80</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>60</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>0</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>OtherPhotos</PhotoType></Photo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>Any guest can use the Health Club (fitness center, jacuzzi, sauna, Turkish bath, indoor swimming pool) and the hotel provides professional massage service. In general this is one of the best 4* in Istanbul, with a  good relation quality/service/price. For location and type of hotel, we recommend it. (JMG 07/08)</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>SurroundingArea</Type><Text>This hotel is ideally located close to the lively and famous Taksim Square and therefore, to the main shopping district of the modern part of Istanbul.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>The medium size rooms are in perfect condition and decorated with taste. The style is modern and has all the necessary facilities for the most comfortable of the stays, such as Interactive TV system with Internet connection,Voice mail system on the telephone, Cable TV and broadcasting in several languages, Minibar, Electronic Safe,  Smoke detectors and sprinklers, Air-conditioning, Pay TV, Computer, internet and fax connection in the rooms. The bathrooms, again, are in perfect condition, clean and are medium size. They have all the following services Hair-dryer, bathtub, bath telephone and bathroom amenities.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>PropertyInformation</Type><Text>The exterior is a modern building in accordance with the area where the hotel is located.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>DiningFacilities</Type><Text>This really good hotel has several restaurants for all taste and needs. The Turkuaz restaurant is one of the selected restaurants of Istanbul, with an extensive menu from Turkish and international cuisine, an attentive service and a spacious atmosphere. There is also the well known Portofino Ristorante an authentic Italian restaurant. For snacks or something lighter, the hotel has the LAP?S BAR where cocktails or good wine can be tasted, for tea and coffee the hotel has the Park Cafe. The hotel has a 24hours room service with an extensive and selected menu.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>Short</Type><Text>The medium size lobby is decorated in modern style, has some seating area to relax and have direct access to the bar &amp; restaurants.</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>Sauna</Code><Text>Sauna</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>BusinessCenter</Code><Text>Business center</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>AirConditioning</Code><Text>Air conditioning</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MiniBarInRoom</Code><Text>Mini-bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HairDryer</Code><Text>Hair dryer</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Gym</Code><Text>Fitness room / Gym</Text></Amenity><Rating><System>Stars</System><Score>40</Score><Description>Four star</Description></Rating><Rank>1</Rank></HotelElement>